data.description: Back on the Market, the buyer's financing fell through! Your Friendly Neighborhood Bald Guy proudly presents 'The Allure of Bellmont'! This 2 bedroom 1 bath home is move-in ready for first-time home buyers, or, if you plan to rent it out, it's ready for your next tenant! And, if you're looking for your next Airbnb, an opportunity awaits! The HVAC and roof are newer (installed in 2021). The home has newer vinyl throughout the entirety of the home. Centrally located, the home is 15 minutes from Armature Works, Ulele, Riverwalk, and Sparkman Wharf! If you want to be close to USF, this home is just under 15 minutes from the campus. If you're interested in a private tour, reach out to Your Friendly Neighborhood Bald Guy!
